### Which @angular/* package(s) are the source of the bug?

Don't known / other

### Is this a regression?

Yes

### Description

The Following SCSS Code works in Production Mode & Development Mode:

`span img {
                height: 78px;
                aspect-ratio: 1;
                pointer-events: none;
                user-select: none;
                animation: rotate var(--duration) infinite forwards linear;
}`

When i move the Animation in a Media Querie in Development Mode it also Works but in Production Mode it doesnt Work anymore.

`@media (hover: none) and (pointer: coarse) {
    button.cursor-button {
        display: block;
        span img {
            animation: rotate var(--duration) infinite forwards linear;
        }
    }
}`

The `rotate` Animation: are a simple rotate animation 

### Please provide a link to a minimal reproduction of the bug

Simple Animation with Media Querie

